Article.ArticleTitle: Molecular docking analysis of COX-2 for potential inhibitors.

AbstractText: Cyclooxygenase-2 (COX-2) is liked with breast cancer. Therefore, it is of interest to design and develop new yet effective compounds against COX-2 from medicinal plants such as the natural alkaloid compounds. We document the optimal binding features of aristolochicacid with COX-2 protein for further consideration.
